sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Activity
    participant OS

    Note over Activity: App is running and in the foreground.
    
    Note over User, OS: System shows a permission dialog.
    OS->>OS: Incoming call or permission request
    OS->>Activity: onPause()
    Note over Activity: Activity is partially visible but not in focus.

    Note over User, OS: User dismisses the dialog.
    User->>OS: Interacts with dialog (e.g., clicks "Allow" or "Deny")
    OS->>Activity: onResume()
    Note over Activity: Activity regains focus and is fully interactive.
